Package com.ibm.mobile.services.push

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IBMPushMessage
    This interface defines the structure of the notification message.
    IBMPushNotificationListener
    This interface defines the method that receives the notification message.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IBMPush
    IBMPush provides methods required by an android application to be able to receive push notifications.
    IBMPushBroadcastReceiver
    IBMPushBroadcastReceiver receives GCM messages and delivers them to com.ibm.mobile.services.push.IBMPushIntentService.
    IBMPushIntentService
    IBMPushIntentService responsible for handling communication from GCM (Google Cloud Messaging).
    IBMSimplePushNotification
    IBMSimplePushNotification denotes the notification message that is sent to the mobile device
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    IBMPushException
    The exception class for all exceptions thrown by IBMPush
